title: Catching You Up on the Tasia & Camo Tea
description:
From the cute and gorgeous to the not so very cute and gorgeous, Tasia and Camo dish on everything that's happened since the last episode. Tasia is getting ready for the baby by buying bougie baby products and dishes on why she's firing the woman who does her eyelashes. Camo talks about his recent trip to LA where he was accosted by some random man, but is still feeling like a brand-new person. Plus, the two discuss why it's not okay to wear "Queen" shirts as a grown adult.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
